column2: SELECT m.cent_gal_ID as ID, m.RA as ra, m.DEC as dec, n.distance as dist, o.nprof as nprof, o.petroR5#_r as Re, p.band as band, p.bin as bin, p.profMean as mean FROM MyDB.CAM_CATALOGUE AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll AS o ON n.objid = o.objid LEFT JOIN PhotoProfile AS p ON n.objid = p.objid
